                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>


            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 gallery-grid gal_c gal_b">
                <div class="gallery-single fix">
                    <div class="post-box">
                        <div class="post-thumb">
                            <img src="~/Content/images/article_photo/photo_02.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="post-img" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-info">
                            <h4>Riding in Traffic</h4>
                            <p>Here you can find out about the rules on riding on roads, overtaking, turning, crossings and trams.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 gallery-grid gal_a gal_c">
                <div class="gallery-single fix">
                    <div class="post-box">
                        <div class="post-thumb">
                            <img src="~/Content/images/article_photo/photo_03.jpg" class="img-fluid" alt="post-img" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="post-info">
                            <h4>Riding on bike lanes and paths</h4>
                            <p>It is important to know what bike lanes and paths look like and the different rules that apply to them.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
